Description: Web UI and CLI to manage sing-box on Keenetic/Entware.
 Accepts a node URI (vless://, hysteria2://, socks5://, ...) and renders
 the corresponding /opt/etc/sing-box/config.json. Provides a 4-tab web
 interface on :8765 with status, settings, logs and backups. Does not
 touch routing or iptables - keen-pbr and the netfilter hooks remain in
 charge.
